H0.text: Traditional Latin pluralization of Latin-originating words ending in 'us' is to replace the 'us' with. a

H1.text: Traditional Latin pluralization of Latin-originating words ending in 'us' is to replace the 'us' with. e

H2.text: Traditional Latin pluralization of Latin-originating words ending in 'us' is to replace the 'us' with. es

H3.text: Traditional Latin pluralization of Latin-originating words ending in 'us' is to replace the 'us' with. i
